                <span>Manually check each response</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>No version control or collaboration</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-red-500 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>Hard to detect regressions</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
          </div>

