              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>PMs can't write tests</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>QA needs to learn YAML syntax</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>Hard to visualize test structure</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
                <span class="text-gray-400 font-bold">✗</span>
                <span>Steep learning curve</span>
